release-notes-*.md
screenshot.png
Screenshot*.png

# Downloaded Binaries (Dependencies)
OnionHop/tor/tor.exe
OnionHop/tor/tor-gencert.exe
OnionHop/tor/geoip
OnionHop/tor/geoip6
